        <p class="MsoNormal"><b>
		<span style="font-size:10.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00663F">
		Perfect Oak Floors</span></b><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
color:#00663F"> - Telephone 01392 &nbsp;861211<o:p> -
		<a href="#Latest_Oak_Flooring_News">News</a></o:p></span></p>
<p>As the UK's leading oak flooring company, we aim to provide the finest machined oak from Germany at unbeatable prices. With years of experience in the industry, we pride ourselves on delivering high quality, solid oak and a faultless service to customers throughout the UK.</p>
<p>Grown and machined in Bavaria, Germany, we believe that our German Character grade 1 oak is the best in the business. Our product never fails to meet the demands of discerning customers.</p>
<p>As well as our oak from Germany, we also import beautiful knot free brown Merbau flooring from Indonesia, and the finest solid hardwood decking from Brazil.</p>
<p>With an extensive stockholding from our suppliers from Germany, we have flooring to suit any style of property. Our flooring can enhance a period property or complement a more minimalist modern interior.</p>
<p>We work closely with all of our customers, to ensure that we source quality products which meet your every demand. We take pride in delivering exemplary customer service, and strongly believe in tailoring our service to suit you and your requirements.</p>
<p>We carry sufficient flooring stock in order to match your supply demand. Please feel free to browse our site or to call 01392 861211 and we'd be delighted to provide you with more information.</p>

