        <blockquote class="style2">
            <p class="style3"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Latest Recommendation.</span> 
			<br />
			<br />
			Dear Martin<br />
			<br />
			We are absolutely thrilled with our oak floor from The Oak Flooring Company.   Having got fed-up with the impracticality of cream carpet, we decided to take the plunge and replace it with oak right through our main living area and we are so pleased that we did.  I had worried that wood flooring might feel cold after fitted carpet but this could not be further from the truth.  The oak has a wonderfully warm honey tone and the detail in the grain is just stunning.  And of course, unlike carpet it reflects the light which is great news if you want more daylight in your home especially during the winter.  It is fabulous to walk on bare-foot and whilst we had intended to put some rugs down, now we simply don't want to cover any of it up!  Investing in such a quality product we decided to use The Oak Flooring Company's recommended fitter to get a really first-class professional finish.  There were some potentially tricky areas to negotiate, steps for example and we didn't want to leave anything to chance.  Again, we couldn't be more delighted with the finished article.  We are also grateful for the personal care and attention shown by The Oak Flooring Company from initial discussions right through the process to completion.  We were well informed and advised at every stage along the way and were never in any doubt as to what was happening next.  This meant that any potential stress was kept to an absolute minimum. </p>
        <ul>
            <li style="text-align: justify;">
			<p>Stockists of Rewmar elastic adhesive for glue down jobs</p>
